  <bodyText><![CDATA[<h2>Explore Lakes and Mountains in the Alps and Beyond</h2>
<p data-pm-slice="1 1 []">Our Lakes and Mountains Holidays take you to some of the most beautiful spots in Europe, where majestic peaks overlook quiet lakeside walks, scenic boat rides, and dining with a view.</p>
<p>Discover the beauty of Europe’s mountain regions, from the mountains of Austria to the crystal clear blue waters of the Italian lakes.</p>
<p data-pm-slice="1 1 []"><a data-udi="umb://document/ed0bcafa85424c78b6325c16c70223f6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ed0bcafa85424c78b6325c16c70223f6}" title="Lakes &amp; Mountains Late Deals">Browse our latest deals for Lake and Mountains holidays</a> and start planning your next unforgettable trip.</p>
<div class="g6">
<p><img style="width: 491px; height: 263px;" src="/media/13086171/ita_como_main_m20-1.jpg?width=491&amp;height=263&amp;mode=max" alt="lakes and mountains holiday" data-udi="umb://media/106f538a36084ec2a17a08a8f22f18de" /></p>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div class="g6">
<h2><strong>Italy </strong><strong> </strong></h2>
<p>Discover the beauty of the Italian Lakes and mountains. With excellent access to hiking trails and wild swimming spots, there’s plenty to uncover.<span> </span></p>
<p><span>We take great pride in offering some of the best countryside retreats in the Lakes, where a slower pace of life, rolling countryside views, and hearty Italian dinners are just a few of the things you can expect when you book with us.</span></p>
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904}" title="Italy">Find out more&gt;&gt;</a></strong></p>
<p> </p>
</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="g6">
<p><img style="width: 474px; height: 254px;" src="/media/13075649/tirolwerbung_928480.jpg?width=474&amp;height=254&amp;mode=max" alt="lakes and mountains holidays" data-udi="umb://media/b4b3ec3c167a478181076af69c7ac8d0" /></p>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div class="g6">
<h2><strong>Austria</strong><strong> </strong></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Austria’s alpine landscape offers a more serene experience than any other part of the country. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">From the deeply carved valleys and alpine peaks to quaint chocolate-box villages and lakeside towns, nowhere else offers such a wide variety of naturally stunning sights.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Get ready to explore, relax and unwind. </span></p>
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/c9325d9a77054a3c8190f3ab0da21760" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c9325d9a77054a3c8190f3ab0da21760}" title="Austria">Find out more&gt;&gt;</a></strong></p>
<p> </p>
</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="g6">
<p><img style="width: 523px; height: 250px;" src="/media/13065907/locarno.jpg?width=523&amp;height=250&amp;mode=max" alt="lakes and mountains holiday" data-udi="umb://media/c79d7fdea0024ff8846173564ea3c7c8" /></p>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div class="g6">
<h2><strong>Switzerland </strong><strong> </strong></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Immerse yourself in the beautiful rocky landscape of Switzerland; where pines and firs tower above precipices and waterfalls. This beautiful region is perfect for gentle sightseeing tours and hiking.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Discover breath-taking landscapes, tranquil lakes and Swiss nature in full bloom. Whatever your interests may be, you’ll find a varied and exciting range of things to do.</span></p>
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/92803bd348ec48c1b64d53e77931172d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/92803bd348ec48c1b64d53e77931172d}" title="Switzerland">Find out more&gt;&gt;</a></strong></p>
<p> </p>
</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="g6">
<p><img style="width: 487px; height: 261px;" src="/media/13085319/lake-bohinj-relaxing-by-lake.jpg?width=487&amp;height=261&amp;mode=max" alt="Lakes and mountains holiday" data-udi="umb://media/b8af47b74d2f4f5b8857418746a127b0" /></p>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div class="g6">
<h2><strong>Slovenia</strong><strong> </strong></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Visit Slovenia, where mountains and lakes abound. Its natural beauty and cultural heritage will take your breath away. </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Taste its traditional food, partake in the colourful local festivals, and admire the beautiful castles, caves and lakes.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">You’ll find an endless amount of activities to enjoy, from cycling and hiking, to strolling through Slovenia's beautiful nature parks and medieval towns.</span></p>
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/eb90f98d70e84089a8cb145d8e46e049" href="/{localLink:umb://document/eb90f98d70e84089a8cb145d8e46e049}" title="Slovenia">Find out more&gt;&gt;</a></strong></p>
<p> </p>
</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="g6">
<p><img style="width: 481px; height: 258px;" src="/media/13082454/otchamonix_gilleslansard-2.jpg?width=481&amp;height=258&amp;mode=max" alt="lakes and mountains holiday" data-udi="umb://media/fd20a3385a4f4d68a34c482f07828148" /></p>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div class="g6">
<h2><strong>France </strong><strong> </strong></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">If you want to enjoy delicious food, fresh mountain air and beautiful scenery, look no further than the French Alps. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Visit beautiful chateaus, walk through picture-perfect landscapes and indulge in excellent food and wine. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Unspoilt villages, breath-taking scenery and glorious sunshine makes this the ultimate summer destination.</span></p>
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/20c1ee89e76c4eab9b98c48479361bdf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/20c1ee89e76c4eab9b98c48479361bdf}" title="France">Find out more&gt;&gt;</a></strong></p>
<p> </p>
</div>
<h2>Get Inspired for Your Next Lakes and Mountains Holiday </h2>
<p> </p>
<div class="g4">
<p><img style="width: 269px; height: 269px;" src="/media/13089609/cycling-holiday.jpeg?width=269&amp;height=269&amp;mode=max" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/810b639fe1d5482f82e05170eea67b7f" /></p>
