<p> </p>
<h2>Plan Your Next Adventure With Us</h2>
<p>Inghams’ summer programme includes a variety of exciting holidays. Including traditional lakes and mountains holidays, <a data-udi="umb://document/5086c9665cf54c2488659f58d6f683e8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5086c9665cf54c2488659f58d6f683e8}" title="Rail Holidays" data-anchor="#">iconic rail tours</a>, walking holidays in Europe, <a data-udi="umb://document/11d9da1aeed54cf09c8dec29e358db37" href="/{localLink:umb://document/11d9da1aeed54cf09c8dec29e358db37}" title="Cycling Holidays" data-anchor="#">cycling holidays</a>, family holidays, coastal holidays, culture excursions and flexible holidays with multiple destinations in one break.</p>
<p>For more information please call <strong>01483 79 11 11</strong></p>]]></bodyText>
